node.text:
🖤🖤 Wow!!! 🖤🖤⁠
⁠
🖤On this day 5 years ago, April 16th, 2016, we opened our doors and poured our first beer. We couldn’t have made it this far without you all, and we truly feel humbled by your faithfulness and support. This past year has been difficult for everyone and we’ve had to adapt constantly, but y’all have shown up for us over and over. 🖤 We have grown and learned so much in these last 5 years and will continue to push ourselves to try new things. Let’s do another 5 my babiez! 😝🖤⁠
⁠
🖤 All Anniversary beers are online now! Head on over to www.theveilbrewing.com/anniversary. We can’t wait to see you and celebrate this special milestone. Again, thank you from the bottom of our hearts. 🙏 🖤

⌛️☠️⚰️🐈 ACT I-III 🐈⚰️☠️⌛️⠀⠀
⠀⠀
⌛️☠️⚰️🐈 The pinnacle of our spirit barrel aged high gravity program is finally ready. 🖤 Sleeping Forever Grand Cru is a blend of 1, 2, and 3 year old Buffalo Trace bourbon barrel aged Sleeping Forever. It has an exceptionally refined depth of barrel character and flavor that only comes with time and careful blending of different vintages. Sleeping Forever Grand Cru will only be released every 5 years and is packaged in matte black bottles, waxed dipped, black velvet labels, wrapped in a custom handkerchief, and laid to rest in special individual boxes with a faux ostrich skin exterior and red velvet interior. All you could ask for in a bourbon barrel aged Imperial Stout - layer upon layer of sweet tobacco, drippy/oily vanilla, melted dark chocolate, top-shelf bourbon, and balanced American oak. 13% ABV ⌛️☠️⚰️🐈⠀⠀

Please check out our last post made earlier today for info about RVA deliveries too. We are hoping to offer NFK delivery starting next week. Also looking into other creative ways to get our cans and bottles into the hands of more Virginians and beyond. Please check out our webstore on our website(www.theveilbrewing.com) and consider purchasing a gift card for future use or some merchandise if possible. Every purchase made right now directly benefits our staff as we continue to find ways to work through these difficult times. Your continued support is greatly appreciated. 🖤

👀New releases! 🍉 
⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
🥤RVA on Tuesday, 8/17🦉
🍦NFK on Wednesday, 8/18🍍

S.U.R.E³ 🍉 🟣🟪

S.U.R.E³ is a triple dry-hopped IPA brewed with Citra, El Dorado, and Simcoe. A neat hop combo leads to saturated vibes of watermelon jolly ranchers, grapefruit gummies, and juicy citrus cream. 6% ABV. $16.50+tax/4pack. 

Show Me 🦉👀 

Show Me is a brand new Double IPA brewed with a big pile of raw wheat and flaked oats then soaked with Citra Cryo, El Dorado, Idaho 7, and Strata hops. Creamy and approachable flavors of hoppy orange candies. 8% ABV. $17.50+tax/4pack. 

Dub Razz Mega Tastee: Xtreme ❤️🥤❤️🥤

Dub Razz Mega Tastee: Xtreme is a brand Imperial Smoothie-style Sour Ale crushed with double raspberry and hit with our proprietary XTREME brewing techniques that make it truly feel like an adult smoothie. A tart and delicious mouthful of raspberries, raspberry jam, and snow cone syrup. 8% ABV. $30.00+tax/4pack. 

Shu (Whipped Cream Raspberry Fluffy Mango Twist) 🥭🍦🍍🍓 

Shu (Whipped Cream Raspberry Fluffy Mango Twist) is a brand new triple fruited Imperial Smoothie Hard Seltzer brewed with our great friends at @omnipollo conditioned with marshmallow, whole vanilla bean, vanilla soft serve ice cream, vanilla salt, plus puréed raspberry, mango, and pineapple. Drenched with flavors of strawberry sugary cereal, berry cobbler with whipped cream on top, and creamsicle candies. 10% ABV. $25.00+tax/4pack. 

NO LIMIT. See ya Tuesday for these!!

👓New releases!🚫⁠
⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠
💐RVA on Tuesday, 8/10☀️⁠
💤NFK on Wednesday, 8/11🐂⁠
⁠
Dusty Roadz 🛣🌪⁠
⁠
Dusty Roadz is our Pale Ale brewed and dry-hopped with Citra, Citra Cryo and Nelson Sauvin hops! Popping out of the glass with dank tropical melon and light crispy crackers. Super crushable. We should make more pale ales. 😉 5.2% ABV. $14.00+tax/4pack.⁠
⁠
Dirt Nap⁴ 🐂 💤 ⁠
⁠
Dirt Nap⁴ is our Double IPA brewed with Galaxy, Citra, Mosaic, and Nelson! Extremely saturated flavors of sweet pineapple, canned peach juice, white grape, and soft papaya. 8.8% ABV. $20.00+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
Remain Bright ☀️👓 ⁠
⁠
Remain Bright is a brand new DIPA brewed with Strata, Mosaic, Citra, Sabro, and Nelson hops. A hoppy flavor ride of pungent fruit, grape skin, fresh apricot, and coconut cream.  8% ABV. $17.50+tax/4pack.⁠
⁠
No More Flowers 🚫💐🚫⁠
⁠
No More Flowers is our beloved Kölsch-inspired beer. Thirst quenching, beautiful, and crispy from 5 weeks of lagering with a distinct soft and delicate ester profile balanced by a light German Tettnang hop addition. 5.2% ABV. $12.00+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
NO LIMIT. See y’all Tuesday for these!
